@defgroup APR_Util APR Utility Functions @{
APU_DECLARE_EXPORT is defined when building the APR-UTIL dynamic library, so that all public symbols are exported.
APU_DECLARE_STATIC is defined when including the APR-UTIL public headers, to provide static linkage when the dynamic library may be unavailable.
APU_DECLARE_STATIC and APU_DECLARE_EXPORT are left undefined when including the APR-UTIL public headers, to import and link the symbols from the dynamic APR-UTIL library and assure appropriate indirection and calling conventions at compile time.
@}

